Benito Gonzalez Jr., 46, was suspended from duty after allegedly exposing his genitals and touching himself inappropriately while seated at a Starbucks in Cherry Hill, New Jersey .
The father-of-three was found guilty of the offense last month and is currently suspended without pay .
A surveillance photo posted to the Cherry Hill police Facebook page led to the arrest .
Gonzalez claims the incident is the culmination of a three-year downward spiral following a traumatic experience more than three years ago .